To install and run:

LINUX & OSX
1) Install firefox: http://getfirefox.com
2) bash < <( curl http://rvm.beginrescueend.com/releases/rvm-install-head )
3) follow rvm post-installation instructions--read them carefully
4) (after opening a new shell) rvm install 1.9.2
5) rvm use 1.9.2
6) gem install bundler
7) bundle install
8) cucumber

WINDOWS
1) Install firefox
2) Download and install JRuby: http://jruby.org
3) Add jruby bin dir to your path
4) Add jruby gem bin dir to your path
5) (from command prompt) jgem install bundler
6) jruby -S bundle install
7) jruby -S cucumber